reviewtext: The dealer had the lowest price: 1/5th of the local office supply store! Love these labels and use it for LOTS more than just labeling files; there's a quote on my desk to remind me to breathe and focus. A tiny strip of plastic, changing a life in a tiny way.Have my baseballs in plexicases with a clear Brother label on each with name and info. This stuff is genius!
summary: Brother's labels are simple, clean and used everywhere.
